        "subject": "LU-897 test: recovery_mds_scale.sh does not use the test framework correctly.",
        "message": "LU-897 test: recovery_mds_scale.sh does not use the test framework correctly.\n\nIt should call run_test for example to start the test and return errors\nappropriately to the framework.\n\nThe changes made remove some additional spurious logging from the start of the\nscript, encapsulate the test within 'test_1', change the exits to be errors so\nthat test framework reports appropriately.\n\nChange-Id: I33e7ef662d49e3d9092b7f016c6c9073d8081c87\nSigned-off-by: Chris Gearing <chris@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
